Women Working In Cannabis: How Alison Gordon Became The CEO Of 48North

When she would walk into meetings about corporate cannabis, Alison Gordon was the only woman in the room. Gordon is now the CEO of 48North, a cannabis company focused on creating products for female users. She shares her story about succeeding in this male-dominated industry and how she hopes to mentor young women in the field.
